&lt;li&gt;Review mechanical drawings, specifications, and submittal documents to ensure proper equipment application and strict compliance with design requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure all product applications and system designs strictly adhere to industry standards and regulatory requirements, including&amp;nbsp;DOE, AHRI, UL, and local building codes, to guarantee safety and performance compliance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare detailed equipment proposals, system selections, and technical recommendations based on specific project conditions and engineering requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
